{"tid":1788764,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"和你lunch 手足收押所外打氣","createTime":"2019-12-19T02:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T03:14:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"30e74a64c69e66488bebc87d05d25b9feb945940","tid":1788764,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:51:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191219/RFPGASVY6R724B25S5TRKU3354/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191219%2FRFPGASVY6R724B25S5TRKU3354%2F&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6rXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=3db956e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191219%2FRFPGASVY6R724B25S5TRKU3354%2F&h=b8e16751\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191219/RFPGASVY6R724B25S5TRKU3354/</a><br />\n<br />\n和你lunch 手足收押所外打氣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191219/large/1576686807_6c2a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191219%2Flarge%2F1576686807_6c2a.gif&h=70fb1c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n參與者經過荔枝角收押所，高叫「手足，加油」。 何家達攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨日分別有近百人參與觀塘和長沙灣「和你lunch」，其中長沙灣人群經過荔枝角收押所，高叫「手足，加油」，警方則出示黃旗及派出近10名防暴警增援。人群向馬路上的警員大叫「上返行人路」，警員未有理會，並開咪指現場舉起標語的市民涉嫌參與非法集結，可能會負上刑事責任。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：保安局拒公開國產TG採購細節<br />\n<br />\n至於觀塘「和你lunch」的參與者遭防暴警驅趕，警員又開咪稱讚自己：「警察加油！多謝！多謝支持警察！」惟現場人士舉起倒豎拇指手勢。警員又干預記者採訪，在執勤期間拿出手機，拍攝記者大頭照片，反問記者：「點解你影我嘅？」記者回應：「可以影你㗎嘛？」警方回應：「可以」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191219/large/1576686807_e837.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191219%2Flarge%2F1576686807_e837.gif&h=546134d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n觀塘和你lunch期間，有警員向市民做出手勢。 何量鈞攝"},{"pid":"670e1ee6cda6d5ee45d7fed62194071b9586d195","tid":1788764,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:51:41.000Z","msg":"社福罷工<br />\n(今日）19/12  1400-1700<br />\n香港人權法案請願遊行<br />\n<br />\n集合地點更新:<br />\n灣仔港灣道海港中心地下(近灣仔游泳池)<br />\n<br />\n遊行路線<br />\n灣仔至中環九國領事館<br />\n<br />\n澳洲領事館+捷克領事館 / 意大利領事館+荷蘭領事館 / 英國領事館 / 美國領事館+歐盟駐港澳辦事處 / 日本領事館 / 加拿大領事館<br />\n<br />\n（不反對通知書已獲批）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（今晚）12月19日 1900<br />\n「堅持才看見希望」行動展望集會<br />\n地點： 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<br />\n(已有不反對通知書)<br />\n社福界罷工委員會"},{"pid":"1f73ee75d2dab797cbe302668fae1735e3a2e71f","tid":1788764,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會忘記手足"},{"pid":"cc31f5db460752b849bb0bcad22214db3c0bc545","tid":1788764,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:53:33.000Z","msg":"香港金總終於接受網上會員申請啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b267946261e449c1d8d98dfd981daa582c13b1ed","tid":1788764,"uid":168020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:56:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c945da94df46da6344f9b0e74096cbdd6b22f090","tid":1788764,"uid":168020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:56:58.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"100a5297c88ccc003a614cd8989c95d825316bdf","tid":1788764,"uid":201605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:58:47.000Z","msg":"長遠要黎一次巴士底"},{"pid":"890ee35a3f4f5e30bbc9a9239126445d0ce3aad7","tid":1788764,"uid":47169,"like"